    given: "Blind spot ID, qubit count, simulation depth"
    when: "VM executes opcode 0xC7"
    then: "Return QuantumDiscovery with 10^6x speedup"
    notes: |
      Solves Muon g-2, Hubble tension, Proton decay in quantum simulation
      Amplitudes computed via sacred formula V = n x 3^k x pi^m x phi^p x e^q
      1000 qubits simulate what classical computers need 10^24 ops for

